  <entry>
    <title>Makefile 学习笔记</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2020/04/14/makefile/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2020/04/14/makefile/</id>
    <published>2020-04-14T13:28:52.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-04-17T03:37:56.849Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="一般工程项目的编译流程"><a href="#一般工程项目的编译流程" class="headerlink" title="一般工程项目的编译流程"></a>一般工程项目的编译流程</h1><h2 id="编译"><a href="#编译" class="headerlink" title="编译"></a>编译</h2><p>首先要把源文件编译成中间代码文件，在Windows下也就是.obj文件，UNIX下是.o文件。</p><h2 id="链接"><a href="#链接" class="headerlink" title="链接"></a>链接</h2><p>将ObjectFile合成执行文件，有时中间目标过多，中间项目需要显式指定中间目标的文件名，很不方便，需要打包为库文件<br>Linux下为.a, Windows下为.lib。</p><h1 id="Makefile语法"><a href="#Makefile语法" class="headerlink" title="Makefile语法"></a>Makefile语法</h1><h2 id="基本语法"><a href="#基本语法" class="headerlink" title="基本语法"></a>基本语法</h2><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">target...:prerequisites...</span></span><br><span class="line">command</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注意，command前有Tab，否则无法执行命令<br>target为目标<br>一般make会显示当前执行的命令，如果希望disable一个command，在前面加上@</p><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@echo <span class="string">"........."</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="使用变量"><a href="#使用变量" class="headerlink" title="使用变量"></a>使用变量</h2><p>定义变量的方法与C++中定义宏的方法类似(原理也类似)<br>使用$调用定义的变量</p><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">OBJECT=main.cpp myvector.cpp</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">execute: <span class="variable">$(OBJECT)</span></span></span><br><span class="line">command</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>同时Makefile支持通配符(*?) </p><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">excute: *.cpp</span></span><br><span class="line">command</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>但是注意变量中如果有通配符,编译时不会展开，会当作字符处理</p><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ERR=*.cpp</span><br><span class="line">CC = g++</span><br><span class="line">CPPFLAG = -Wall -g -std=c++11</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">target:<span class="variable">$(ERR)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$(CC)</span> <span class="variable">$(CPPFLAG)</span> <span class="variable">$(ERR)</span> -o target</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里会直接编译一个名为*.cpp的文件导致报错</p><h3 id="模式变量与目标变量"><a href="#模式变量与目标变量" class="headerlink" title="模式变量与目标变量"></a>模式变量与目标变量</h3><p>对于特定匹配的模式使用不同的变量值</p><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">prog : CFLAGS = -g</span><br><span class="line">prog : prog.o foo.o bar.o</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable">$(CC)</span> <span class="variable">$(CFLAGS)</span> prog.o foo.o bar.o</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">prog.o : prog.c</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable">$(CC)</span> <span class="variable">$(CFLAGS)</span> prog.c</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">foo.o : foo.c</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable">$(CC)</span> <span class="variable">$(CFLAGS)</span> foo.c</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">bar.o : bar.c</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable">$(CC)</span> <span class="variable">$(CFLAGS)</span> bar.c</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>模式变量更为泛化</p><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">%.o : CFLAGS = -O</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="多种赋值语句"><a href="#多种赋值语句" class="headerlink" title="多种赋值语句"></a>多种赋值语句</h3><h4 id><a href="#" class="headerlink" title=":="></a>:=</h4><p>  循环定义会使得文件发生错误<br>  <figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">A = <span class="variable">$(B)</span></span><br><span class="line">B = <span class="variable">$(A)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>  如果想要覆盖定义，使用<code>:=</code>符号 来定义<br>  <figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x := foo</span><br><span class="line">y := <span class="variable">$(x)</span> bar</span><br><span class="line">x := later</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>  该方法定义的变量只能调用在语句之前定义的变量，从而避免紊乱</p><h4 id="-1"><a href="#-1" class="headerlink" title="?="></a>?=</h4><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">A ?= B</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这个定义的方法含义为：如果A没有被定义，那么定义A=B</p><h4 id="-2"><a href="#-2" class="headerlink" title="+="></a>+=</h4><p>如果变量之前没有定义过，那么，“+=”会自动变成“=”，如果前面有变量定义，那么“+=”会继承于前次操作的赋值符。如果前一次的是“:=”，那么“+=”会以“:=”作为其赋值符，如： </p><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">variable := value</span><br><span class="line">variable += more</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此时variable = variable more</p><h3 id="advanced-高级变量用法"><a href="#advanced-高级变量用法" class="headerlink" title="(advanced)高级变量用法"></a>(advanced)高级变量用法</h3><h4 id="变量替换"><a href="#变量替换" class="headerlink" title="变量替换"></a>变量替换</h4><p>  语法<code>$(var:a=b)</code>或者<code>${var:a=b}</code>替换var中以a <code>结尾</code> 的词组将a替换为b<br>  <figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">foo := a.o b.o c.o</span><br><span class="line">bar := $(foo:.o=.c)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>  bar = a.c b.c c.c</p><h4 id="变量嵌套"><a href="#变量嵌套" class="headerlink" title="变量嵌套"></a>变量嵌套</h4><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = y</span><br><span class="line">y = z</span><br><span class="line">z = u</span><br><span class="line">a := $($(<span class="variable">$(x)</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>简单特性，不多言<br>显然a = u</p><h4 id="变量拼接"><a href="#变量拼接" class="headerlink" title="变量拼接"></a>变量拼接</h4><p>形式$(a)&lt;expr&gt;</p><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a = first</span><br><span class="line">b = second</span><br><span class="line">all = $a_$b</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>由于变量本身是宏，同样很好推导<br>all = first_second</p><h2 id="Make嵌套执行与变量传递"><a href="#Make嵌套执行与变量传递" class="headerlink" title="Make嵌套执行与变量传递"></a>Make嵌套执行与变量传递</h2><p>大型项目中，我们会把我们不同模块或是不同功能的源文件放在不同的目录中，我们可以在每个目录中都书写一个该目录的Makefile，这有利于让我们的Makefile变得更加地简洁</p><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">subpro:</span></span><br><span class="line">cd subproj &amp;&amp; <span class="variable">$(MAKE)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>该方法与下述方法等价</p><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">subpro:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$(MAKE)</span> -C subproj</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>同时如果希望子项目的makefile继承变量，使用一下语法</p><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> &lt;var&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>或者在定义完全部后使用</p><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;var1&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;var2&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果不许要继承</p><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">unexport</span> &lt;var&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="自动推导"><a href="#自动推导" class="headerlink" title="自动推导"></a>自动推导</h2>]]></content>
    
