  <entry>
    <title>emacs构建前端开发环境并添加firefox-dev支持</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2020/03/29/emacs-web/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2020/03/29/emacs-web/</id>
    <published>2020-03-29T11:34:28.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-04-07T07:03:32.768Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="excerpt">    <img src="/2020/03/29/emacs-web/a.png"></div><a id="more"></a>  <h1 id="起因"><a href="#起因" class="headerlink" title="起因"></a>起因</h1><p>最近对javascript的函数式语法产生了兴趣，决定学习一下<br>学习js难免要和前端打交道，目前好用的前端编辑器有很多，sublime，vsc，atom，vim都是很不错的选择，但是对于一个常年使用emacs的用户来说，总觉得小拇指不有点不适应，花了半天的时间参考了一些配置，做了一个有基本功能的开发环境。  </p><h1 id="HTML与CSS–web-mode"><a href="#HTML与CSS–web-mode" class="headerlink" title="HTML与CSS–web mode"></a>HTML与CSS–web mode</h1><p>  html文件和css的配置并不复杂，并且有很好的工具，web-mode基本上就是开箱即,用很方便，而且支持目前大部分主流的模板文件y以及css格式，相关配置如下，力求最小化配置，如果有需要可以阅读官网的document进行一些个性化配置。<a href="http://web-mode.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">web-mode</a></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(use-package web-mode</span><br><span class="line">  :ensure t</span><br><span class="line">  :mode &quot;\\.[px]?html?\\&#39;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :mode &quot;\\.\\(?:tpl\\|blade\\)\\(?:\\.php\\)?\\&#39;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :mode &quot;\\.erb\\&#39;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :mode &quot;\\.eex\\&#39;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :mode &quot;\\.jsp\\&#39;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :mode &quot;\\.as[cp]x\\&#39;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :mode &quot;\\.hbs\\&#39;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :mode &quot;\\.mustache\\&#39;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :mode &quot;\\.svelte\\&#39;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :mode &quot;\\.vue\\&#39;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :mode &quot;\\.twig\\&#39;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :mode &quot;\\.jinja\\&#39;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :mode &quot;wp-content&#x2F;themes&#x2F;.+&#x2F;.+\\.php\\&#39;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :mode &quot;templates&#x2F;.+\\.php\\&#39;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :mode &quot;\\.tsx\\&#39;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :mode &quot;\\.swig\\&#39;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :config</span><br><span class="line">  (setq web-mode-markup-indent-offset 2</span><br><span class="line">web-mode-css-indent-offset 2</span><br><span class="line">web-mode-code-indent-offset 2</span><br><span class="line">web-mode-enable-current-element-highlight t;对光标所在的元素进行高亮提示</span><br><span class="line">web-mode-enable-css-colorization t);css色彩显示</span><br><span class="line">)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果你需要自动补全可以使用company-web,虽然我觉得并没有什么必要</p><h1 id="javascript–补全与设置"><a href="#javascript–补全与设置" class="headerlink" title="javascript–补全与设置"></a>javascript–补全与设置</h1><h2 id="skewer踩坑"><a href="#skewer踩坑" class="headerlink" title="skewer踩坑"></a>skewer踩坑</h2><p>  最早在google上搜索的时候，推荐给我的是skewer-mode，这个插件看起来十分诱人，但其实有着很大的缺陷</p><ol><li>已经维护较少<br>最近的更新是在8个月以前，对于快速更新的前端技术来说是一个已经很不活跃的项目了，相关项目下的issue也没有人解决。</li><li>奇怪的bug<br>其卖点live develop功能在尝试后发现有重大缺陷，html文件不能预览，甚至连基本的tag都无法执行。</li><li>过于臃肿<br>这个问题已经是一个老问题了，社区的反映也很多，许多emacs配置已经放弃了这个包。  </li></ol><h2 id="impatient-mode-的问题"><a href="#impatient-mode-的问题" class="headerlink" title="impatient mode 的问题"></a>impatient mode 的问题</h2><p>  skewer-mode的作者有另一个包用于html预览–impatient-mode<br>  这个mode同样很诱人，能够直接实时预览你的html文件，甚至不用保存，性能也好，但是有一个问题，html中如果包含有js文件，js文件的修改并不能刷新页面只能手动刷新，我是个懒人，这么费尽的事情我当然不愿意做，所以才有下面的内容。  </p><h2 id="更好的选择–browser-sync"><a href="#更好的选择–browser-sync" class="headerlink" title="更好的选择–browser-sync"></a>更好的选择–browser-sync</h2><p>  实际上在我一番探索后，emacs内部并没有很好的解决方案，几次搜索之后看上了这个有趣的项目<a href="http://www.browsersync.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">browser-sync</a>尝试之后发现这个包的确好用。安装过程也很简单。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g browser-sync</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装之后在命令行下启动就行</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">browser-sync start --server --files <span class="string">"css/*.css, *.html"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这个命令会启动一个服务器监听css文件夹下*.css文件和 当前文件夹下 *.html的变化并打开浏览器预览，如果有变化会刷新浏览器。<br>当然我们希望所有的文件都能被监听。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">browser-sync start --server --files <span class="string">"**/*.css, **/*.html, **/*.js"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这个命令可以监听当前文件夹下所有的css，html，js文件，只要有修改，浏览器就会马上刷新。<br>我们只需要在命令行中调用这个命令就行了，但是这样有点不方便，我们希望编辑器中能直接使用这个命令，对于emacser来说，添加一个函数就行了～</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(defun browser-sync ()</span><br><span class="line">  (interactive)</span><br><span class="line">  (async-shell-command &quot;browser-sync start --server --files \&quot;**&#x2F;*.css, **&#x2F;*.html,**&#x2F;*.js\&quot;&quot;))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>好了，每次需要预览的时候<code>M-x browser-sync RET</code>就好了。<br>当然如果你希望打开一个项目的时候就启动，可以使用LSP来识别项目并在项目打开的时候启用命令，这里我就不展开了。</p><h2 id="lsp-补全"><a href="#lsp-补全" class="headerlink" title="lsp-补全"></a>lsp-补全</h2><p>关于emacs的补全我就不多费口舌了，我使用的是company+lsp（巨硬NB！）<br>使用lsp进行补全需要下载相关的language-server，我使用的是typescript的language-server。安装指令如下</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm i -g typescript-language-server; npm i -g typescript</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>lsp和company的配置我就不赘述了，有很多的介绍。</p><h1 id="添加firefox-developer-edition支持，并设置为默认浏览器"><a href="#添加firefox-developer-edition支持，并设置为默认浏览器" class="headerlink" title="添加firefox-developer-edition支持，并设置为默认浏览器"></a>添加firefox-developer-edition支持，并设置为默认浏览器</h1><p>不得不说firefox的开发者版本真香，个人觉得比chromium还好用，不过emacs中并不直接支持使用，有如下两个方案  </p><ol><li>设置系统的默认浏览器为firefox-developer-edition</li><li>修改emacs的默认配置 </li></ol><p>emacs中配置默认的浏览器实际上是设置一个variable,<code>browse-url-browser-function</code>直接调用一个函数用于启动浏览器（可以看作是一种closure）</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(setq browse-url-browser-function &#39;values)</span><br><span class="line">;; values 有几个可选值</span><br><span class="line">;; browse-url-mozilla                 Mozilla     Don&#39;t know</span><br><span class="line">;; browse-url-firefox                 Firefox     Don&#39;t know (tried with 1.0.1)</span><br><span class="line">;; browse-url-chrome                  Chrome      47.0.2526.111</span><br><span class="line">;; browse-url-chromium                Chromium    3.0</span><br><span class="line">;; browse-url-epiphany                Epiphany    Don&#39;t know</span><br><span class="line">;; browse-url-conkeror                Conkeror    Don&#39;t know</span><br><span class="line">;; browse-url-w3                      w3          0</span><br><span class="line">;; browse-url-text-*              Any text browser     0</span><br><span class="line">;; browse-url-generic                 arbitrary</span><br><span class="line">;; browse-url-default-windows-browser MS-Windows browser</span><br><span class="line">;; browse-url-default-macosx-browser  macOS browser</span><br><span class="line">;; browse-url-xdg-open                freedesktop.org xdg-open</span><br><span class="line">;; browse-url-kde                     KDE konqueror (kfm)</span><br><span class="line">;; browse-url-elinks                  Elinks      Don&#39;t know (tried with 0.12.GIT)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>设置好之后使用<code>browse-url-***</code>相关的命令便可以用设置的浏览器打开网站或者文件，但是目前来看没有专门为firefox-dev设置一个函数，我设置为browse-url-mozilla后也没有用firefox-dev打开，chromium都有。。。<br>于是决定自己写一个函数来用，稍微修改了一下brow-url-firefox并且copy到了我的配置文件中     </p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(defcustom browse-url-firefox-dev-program</span><br><span class="line">  (let ((candidates &#39;(&quot;icecat&quot; &quot;iceweasel&quot; &quot;firefox-developer-edition&quot;)))</span><br><span class="line">    (while (and candidates (not (executable-find (car candidates))))</span><br><span class="line">      (setq candidates (cdr candidates)))</span><br><span class="line">    (or (car candidates) &quot;firefox-developer-edition&quot;))</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;The name by which to invoke Firefox-dev or a variant of it.&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :type &#39;string)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">(defun browse-url-firefox-dev (url &amp;optional new-window)</span><br><span class="line">  (interactive (browse-url-interactive-arg &quot;URL: &quot;))</span><br><span class="line">  (setq url (browse-url-encode-url url))</span><br><span class="line">  (let* ((process-environment (browse-url-process-environment)))</span><br><span class="line">    (apply &#39;start-process</span><br><span class="line">           (concat &quot;firefox-developer-edition &quot; url) nil</span><br><span class="line">           browse-url-firefox-dev-program</span><br><span class="line">           (append</span><br><span class="line">            browse-url-firefox-arguments</span><br><span class="line">            (if (browse-url-maybe-new-window new-window)</span><br><span class="line">(if browse-url-firefox-new-window-is-tab</span><br><span class="line">    &#39;(&quot;-new-tab&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">  &#39;(&quot;-new-window&quot;)))</span><br><span class="line">            (list url)))))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这样就大功告成了！<br>Happy Hacking!</p>]]></content>
    
